		<title>Mayo Clinic Q&amp;#038;A: What does it mean to be in a cancer clinical trial?</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-qa-what-does-it-mean-to-be-in-a-cancer-clinical-trial/</link>
		
